Face/Off is an excellent movie and stars john travolta and nicholas cage. the movie is well directed by james woo and well acted by john and nick. the story is amazing and the movie is full of suspense and action. this is probably one of the best action movies ever and one of the best films with nick cage. i really enjoyed this movie and you will to. this movie is cinematastic. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do
